<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Rule 37 of the Federal Rules of Criminal Procedure was abrogated <date date="1967-12-04">Dec. 4, 1967</date>, eff. <date date="1968-07-01">July 1, 1968</date>. Provisions of such former rule for certiorari are covered by rule 19 et seq. of the Rules of the United States Supreme Court.</p>
